high_descs: Walk to the coffee maker on the end of the counter.
Grab the spoon from the counter.
Go to the stove and focus on the top left burner.
Place the spoon in the pan.
Grab the pan from the stove.
Turn around and go to the kitchen sink.
Place the pan and spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon and pan into the sink at once.

high_descs: Go to the counter right of the stove
Pick up a spoon on the counter
Go to the stove
Place the spoon in a pan
Pick up the pan from the stove
Turn to the sink
Place the pan and spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a pan and spoon in a sink

high_descs: Turn right, proceed to wall.  Turn left to face counter with coffee maker on it.
Pick up spoon from counter, behind shaker.
Turn left, proceed to stove on right.  Turn right to face stove.
Put spoon standing up in pan on right back burner of stove.
Pick up pan with spoon from right back burner of stove.
Turn around and go to sink.
Put pan with spoon in center of sink.
anns.task_desc: Move spoon to pan on stove, move both to sink.
